> Comparison of Selenium and Playwright:

ALL Actions:
------------
  > Installation:
    Selenium: pip install selenium
    Playwright: pip install playwright, then playwright install

  > Browser and Package control:
    Launch browser:
     Selenium: driver = webdriver.Chrome()
     Playwright: browser = playwright.chromium.launch()

  > Open URL:
    Selenium: driver.get("https://example.com")
    Playwright: page.goto("https://example.com")

  > Get page title:
    Selenium: title = driver.title
    Playwright: title = page.title()

  > Get Current URL:
    Selenium: current_url = driver.current_url
    Playwright: current_url = page.url

  > Refresh page:
    Selenium: driver.refresh()
    Playwright: page.reload()

  > Close Tab/Window:
    Selenium: driver.close()
    Playwright: page.close()

  > Quit Browser:
    Selenium: driver.quit()
    Playwright: browser.close()